parameters: Stop it! Hey...where are you touching...?!

In the sinking consciousness, only Miiru's voice
calling for help could be heard...

I was caught by the monster, and even Aeru, who
tried to help me, was done in.

Even though I tried shouting let go, there was no
way my words would reach the monster.
Just letting several tentacles crawl over my body

Somehow, the surface is slimy and it feels really
gross.
Stop it! Let go already! This! This!

Despite struggling with all my might, kicking and
flailing my body, the tentacles still remained
entwined.

The tentacles, which were just restraining me,
started to move slimily while oozing out mucus.

The tentacles crawled all over me, and my body
reacted with an unfamiliar sensation, making me
tremble.
Nn... Stop it, I said... Ahh \i[249]

The monster, as usual, didn't say a word and just
let its tentacles crawl over my body.

I'm sure this guy knows exactly where to touch me
to get a reaction.

With each of the tentacles searching, the sound of
my pounding heart, the heat escaping from my skin,
and my trembling breath... all of it

The more I try to endure it so it doesn't show,
the more my entire body ends up being focused on
it.

So, how I'm feeling right now, which is more
likely to be exposed.

After a while, the tentacles began to attack only
my lower body.

The area between my crotch is already sticky, but
it's definitely not just because of the tentacle's
slime.
Sweet, sweet nectar is dripping from my body...

The movements of the tentacles seem to be
carefully sipping that nectar.

The mouth, constantly releasing sighs, was always
open, and I had even stopped caring about the
drool dripping from it.

Right now, I just wish for this state to end as
soon as possible, even if it's just for a second.

Tentacles are invading from the slackly open
mouth.

Just when I thought it was thrust deeply into my
throat, it would pull back towards the front
again.

I desperately moved my mouth to somehow push back
the invading foreign object.

However, those tentacles, seeming to be many times
the size of my tongue, rampage arrogantly inside
my mouth.

I no longer have the will to resist, I just accept
the tentacles violating my mouth.

The monster seemed to have sensed that, and its
movements were not as violent as before.

It is moving back and forth inside the mouth at a
steady rhythm.

However, that didn't last long, and the already
large tentacles swelled even more... and

For a moment, my mind went blank and I felt like I
was losing consciousness, but the pain of the
liquid poured into my mouth quickly brought me
back to reality.

I'm just in pain... I can't breathe, so I
desperately resist.

However, this time the tentacles are thrust into
the back of my throat, and it feels like my body
is being penetrated more roughly than before.

It's painful, so painful... I finally couldn't
bear the pain any longer.

Why do I have to go through this pain when I
haven't done anything wrong... I hate suffering
like this...

Before I knew it, tears were flowing from both of
my eyes. Once the tears started to flow, they
continued to overflow without stopping.

The tentacles that were wrapped around my body
suddenly loosened.

I just stare blankly at the monster, not knowing
what's happening anymore.

As I continued to watch for a while, I heard
someone's voice.

Did this guy just say that? Because you looked
cute, what's up with that?

I was planning to make you cry... but I
couldn't... I'm sorry...
Thank you for being okay... Thank you

Until the very end, doing as it pleases, monsters
are the worst!!
I don't want to hear that from you!!
When I look at my body, it's completely soaked.
